        "y": -520
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# First Ring Grammar\n\nThe first circle should be grouped into four stable sectors:\n\n- **Layout**: beautify, reroute, align, spacing\n- **Node Palette**: create, connect, palette entry\n- **Info**: inspect, reveal source, provenance\n- **Mode**: select, connect, edit, present\n\nThis keeps the radial menu compact enough for fast use while preserving a readable structure.",
        "definitionKey": "markdown"
      }
    },
